  "3025880": {
    "name": "Argonauts Path",
    "steam_appid": 3025880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个令人难以置信且快速的<strong>Roguelike</strong>卡牌构筑游戏，你很可能会死亡或成为英雄，但大概率是前者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/83b8033acf2f11c10a0c49fb6355cd6a.poster.avif?t=1746193667\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/83b8033acf2f11c10a0c49fb6355cd6a.webm?t=1746193667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/83b8033acf2f11c10a0c49fb6355cd6a.mp4?t=1746193667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将穿越萨摩瑟雷尔地区，从村庄到村庄，在战斗与成长的道路上前行，最终放逐一位神明，并守护人类300年。英雄们已经与阿尔戈斯（最重要的神圣神器，它记录你的时间，让你在死亡后重返那个时刻）绑定。你将选择他们，并展开一场拯救人类的战斗，对抗七位神明，这些堕落的神拥有支配人类的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/d1bad0c2c262038c68a4a3383668058d.poster.avif?t=1746193667\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/d1bad0c2c262038c68a4a3383668058d.webm?t=1746193667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/d1bad0c2c262038c68a4a3383668058d.mp4?t=1746193667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将经过7个村庄，完成任务并找到3个支援元素。你将与英雄一起成长，每升一级，你可以从两种神圣祝福中选择一种。每个村庄的任务以及任务中获得特殊奖励的可能性都取决于你的运气，这与祝福（对游戏玩法有很大影响）相结合，确保每次游戏都独特而新颖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/21e7e28cf946ac583406753ba677bf2a.poster.avif?t=1746193667\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/21e7e28cf946ac583406753ba677bf2a.webm?t=1746193667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/21e7e28cf946ac583406753ba677bf2a.mp4?t=1746193667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村庄中的支援元素：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>商人</strong>（你可以购买3张卡牌）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>萨满</strong>（你可以删除或升级卡牌，第一次免费）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spa</strong>（你可以恢复全部或一半的生命值）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神器</strong>（第一次使用它会增加你的基础生命值和能量，之后每次使用会以一些生命为代价增加你的最大生命值）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务主要是与敌人的战斗遭遇，分为不同的等级：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第1村庄 - 1级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第2村庄 - 2级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第3村庄 - 2级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第4村庄 - 3级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第5村庄 - 4级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第6村庄 - 4级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第7村庄 - 5级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三位堕落者之一。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/953f7fcbfccdd24a7b2aee3901e30753.poster.avif?t=1746193667\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/953f7fcbfccdd24a7b2aee3901e30753.webm?t=1746193667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025880/extras/953f7fcbfccdd24a7b2aee3901e30753.mp4?t=1746193667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此，任务有时会让你面临可能致命的艰难遭遇。你必须权衡自己是否准备好接受挑战，通过对抗敌人变得更强大，或者继续前进，让未来的遭遇变得更加困难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
